OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1778357153
OL,3,C'Puffin cam' returns to give viewers
OL,4,Cbird's eye view of the Farne Islands
OL,6,FNature lovers will be able to watch
OL,7,Fseabirds returning to breed on the
OL,8,FFarne Islands as "puffin-cams" go live
OL,9,Ffor a second year on the nature
OL,10,Freserve.
OL,12,FThe National Trust said its live,
OL,13,Fremote cameras will give viewers a
OL,14,Ffront row seat to the lives and
OL,15,Fbreeding season of some of the 200,000
OL,16,Fseabirds that make their home on the
OL,17,Fislands off the coast of
OL,18,FNorthumberland.
OL,26,@pD@ROUpD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1778357153
OL,3,C'Puffin cam' returns to give viewers
OL,4,Cbird's eye view of the Farne Islands
OL,6,FAlong with the live stream of the
OL,7,Fpuffins, a second camera is trained on
OL,8,Fthe guillemots which roost and nest on
OL,9,Fthe cliffs of the islands.
OL,11,FLaura Knowles, visitor operations
OL,12,Fmanager for the National Trust, said:
OL,13,F"The breeding season is always a
OL,14,Fspecial time of year as our ranger
OL,15,Fteams gear up to monitor the birds
OL,16,Fdaily over the spring and summer
OL,17,Fmonths.
OL,19,F"We're thrilled to bring puffin cam
OL,20,Fback for a second season.
OL,26,@uD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1778357153
OL,3,C'Puffin cam' returns to give viewers
OL,4,Cbird's eye view of the Farne Islands
OL,6,F"Last year the live cams attracted
OL,7,Fover a quarter of a million views, and
OL,8,Fwe were overwhelmed by the incredible
OL,9,Fmessages from people across the world
OL,10,Fwho tuned in to watch the puffins go
OL,11,Fabout their daily lives.
OL,13,F"It was wonderful to see how deeply
OL,14,Fthe live stream connected viewers to
OL,15,Fthe Farnes, especially those who may
OL,16,Fnever have the chance to visit in
OL,17,Fperson."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUyD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1778357153
OL,3,C'Puffin cam' returns to give viewers
OL,4,Cbird's eye view of the Farne Islands
OL,6,FRangers will be conducting bird counts
OL,7,Fnext month to see how the various
OL,8,Fspecies have fared in the wake of bird
OL,9,Fflu, which hit the colonies hard in
OL,10,F2022 and 2023, and a series of storms
OL,11,Fearlier this year.
OL,13,FThey will also be looking out for
OL,14,Fpuffins ringed last year to help
OL,15,Fassess survival rates and track how
OL,16,Fbirds are faring.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1778357153
OL,3,C'Puffin cam' returns to give viewers
OL,4,Cbird's eye view of the Farne Islands
OL,6,FSophia Jackson, area ranger for the
OL,7,FNational Trust on the Farne Islands,
OL,8,Fsaid: "We've been closely monitoring
OL,9,Fthe impact of bird flu as part of
OL,10,Finternational research into the
OL,11,Fdisease.
OL,13,F"In 2022 we recorded over 6,000 dead
OL,14,Fbirds, and more than 3,500 in 2023.
OL,16,F"Comparing that to fewer than 10 in
OL,17,F2025 suggests things may be improving,
OL,18,Fbut we can never let our guard down."
OL,26,@pD@GOUuD@AOUxD@AOUzD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1778357153
OL,3,C'Puffin cam' returns to give viewers
OL,4,Cbird's eye view of the Farne Islands
OL,6,FAnd Ben McCarthy, head of nature
OL,7,Fconservation at the National Trust,
OL,8,Fsaid storms Goretti, Ingrid and
OL,9,FChandra caused "floods and devastation
OL,10,Ffor both humans and wildlife" and
OL,11,Fbattered the Atlantic coast of the UK
OL,12,Fand Europe at the beginning of the
OL,13,Fyear.
OL,26,@qD@POUrD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
