OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1778357153
OL,3,C'Puffin cam' returns to give viewers
OL,4,Cbird's eye view of the Farne Islands
OL,6,F"Long-term monitoring collected
OL,7,Fthrough the Seabird Monitoring
OL,8,FProgramme clearly demonstrates the
OL,9,Fimpact of such stormy weather on
OL,10,Fseabird's ability to feed, with
OL,11,Fresulting loss in condition and, in
OL,12,Fworst case scenarios, so called
OL,13,F'wrecks' where birds are washed ashore
OL,14,Fdead or dying.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
