OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1778357153
OL,3,C'Puffin cam' returns to give viewers
OL,4,Cbird's eye view of the Farne Islands
OL,6,F"We don't yet know what this means for
OL,7,Fthe puffin and other seabirds which
OL,8,Fare returning to breed on the Farnes
OL,9,Fthis year, but this makes these counts
OL,10,Feven more important when put in
OL,11,Fcontext with the more extreme weather
OL,12,Four wildlife is also battling against
OL,13,Fdue to climate change," he said.
OL,15,FThe National Trust has also reopened
OL,16,Fthe Farne Islands for the season, with
OL,17,Fvisitor boats now landing on the
OL,18,Fislands, the charity said.
OL,20,FViewers can watch the live stream here.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@WO]
